sections.heading: practice of law; penalty.Except as provided in section 7-101
sections.text: 01, no person shall practice as an attorney or counselor at law, or commence, conduct or defend any action or proceeding to which he is not a party, either by using or subscribing his own name, or the name of any other person, or by drawin
